OL,6,FMPs are set to vote for the first time
OL,7,Fon the government's legislation which
OL,8,Fwill see the lifting of the
OL,9,Fcontroversial two-child benefit cap.
OL,11,FThe move has long been called for and
OL,12,Fwas announced by Chancellor Rachel
OL,13,FReeves in the autumn budget last year.
OL,15,FAround 400,000 fewer children will be
OL,16,Fliving in poverty this April compared
OL,17,Fwith 12 months earlier as a result of
OL,18,Fthe change, according to analysis by
OL,19,Fthe Joseph Rowntree Foundation (JRF).
