OL,6,FHowever, it warned progress on
OL,7,Ftackling poverty is likely to stall if
OL,8,Fthe axe is not followed up with more
OL,9,Faction.
OL,11,F"Without further changes, relative
OL,12,Fpoverty levels remain stuck at a high
OL,13,Flevel after April 2026," the JRF said.
OL,15,FChildren's doctors, teachers, health
OL,16,Fvisitors and anti-poverty charities
OL,17,Fhave called on MPs to vote in support
OL,18,Fof ending the policy.
