OL,6,FA statement issued on behalf of 63
OL,7,Forganisations, including the Child
OL,8,FPoverty Action Group, Citizens Advice,
OL,9,Fthe Royal College of Paediatrics and
OL,10,FChild Health, and teaching union
OL,11,FNASUWT described the cap as "an awful
OL,12,Fexperiment that hurt children".
OL,14,FIt added: "More than any other policy,
OL,15,Fthe two-child limit is responsible for
OL,16,Fdriving child poverty to its current
OL,17,Frecord high.
