OL,6,F"Poverty has a devastating impact on
OL,7,Fyoung lives. Children going without
OL,8,Fthings they need to learn and grow,
OL,9,Fliving in damp homes, struggling at
OL,10,Fschool, facing isolation and stress.
OL,12,F"Today marks the moment when we start
OL,13,Fto turn things around for the next
OL,14,Fgeneration. We commend the Government
OL,15,Ffor making the choice to scrap the two-
OL,16,Fchild limit and ask all MPs to stand
OL,17,Fwith children and support this Bill."
